        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2011-08-18 17:17:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3fb15924-c9bd-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
