      "message": "Patch Set 4: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4bc34b06-d07e-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
