      },
      "date": "2011-09-02 22:24:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(2 inline comments)\n\nThis could be cleaned up a bit.  I wouldn't object to some comment blocks being added to the lmv_ functions being modified to explain them a bit.\n\nIn any case, I don't see how this relates to the statahead patch?  It doesn't necessarily need to be a dependency for the later statahead patches.  The fewer unnecessary patch dependencies there are, the less work it is to update and review the patches, and less work on our overburdened test systems to retest a whole patch series even if most of the patches are not changing.",
